ECHO ===== STUDENTS DATE FIELDS + DATE ALGEBRA =====
LOCATE FOR LNAME = "TAYLOR"
TUPLE DOB
TUPLE ENROLL_D
CALC DOB
CALC (DOB + 1)
CALC (DOB - 1)
CALC DATEADD(DOB, 30)
CALC DATEDIFF(DATE(), DOB)
CALC (DATE() - DOB)
ECHO [CANARY DATEDIFF-MATCH] Expect .T.:
CALC (DATEDIFF(DATE(), DOB) = (DATE() - DOB))

ECHO ===== RELATIONS ENGINE =====
REL LIST
REL CLEAR ALL
REL ADD STUDENTS ENROLL ON SID
REL ADD ENROLL CLASSES ON CLS_ID
REL LIST
REL REFRESH

ECHO ===== TUPLE CROSS-AREA (AREA REFS MUST MATCH REAL FIELDS) =====
ECHO [CANARY TUPLE-AREAREF] Expect area refs to resolve:
SELECT STUDENTS
LOCATE FOR LNAME = "TAYLOR"
TUPLE *
TUPLE LNAME,FNAME
TUPLE #11.*          * TERMS (TERM/START/END)
TUPLE #10.LNAME      * TEACHERS.LNAME (safe field reference)
TUPTALK

ECHO ===== TABLE BUFFER CANARY =====
SELECT STUDENTS
LOCATE FOR LNAME = "TAYLOR"
LIST 1
TUPLE *
TABLE ON
REPLACE FNAME WITH "DeraldNew"
ECHO [CANARY BUF-VIS-1] TUPLE shows buffer immediately:
TUPLE *
ECHO [CANARY BUF-VIS-2] LIST still shows DBF until COMMIT:
LIST 1
COMMIT
ECHO [CANARY BUF-VIS-3] LIST now reflects committed value:
LIST 1

REPLACE FNAME WITH "Derald"
COMMIT
TABLE OFF
LIST 1

ECHO ===== CALCWRITE REVERSIBLE WRITE (GPA +/- 0.01) =====
SELECT STUDENTS
LOCATE FOR LNAME = "TAYLOR"
TABLE ON
TUPLE GPA
ECHO [CANARY CALCWRITE +] Expect GPA to increase by 0.01 after COMMIT:
CALCWRITE GPA = GPA + 0.01
COMMIT
LIST 1
ECHO [CANARY CALCWRITE -] Expect GPA to return after COMMIT:
CALCWRITE GPA = GPA - 0.01
COMMIT
LIST 1
TABLE OFF

